title: First impeachment trial of Donald Trump
deleted: In February 2020, Republican Senator [[Rand Paul]] criticized [[YouTube]] for removing a video of his floor speech about the impeachment trial of Donald Trump. His speech contained a controversial question for impeachment manager [[Adam Schiff]] and counsel for the president: "Are you aware that House Intelligence Committee staffer Shawn Misko had a close relationship with [...] when at the National Security Council together?"
